---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon';
---

<div class="bg-navy section flex flex-wrap justify-center">
  <div class="section-content">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h6 class="m-0 text-red text-xs uppercase">Get to know us</h6>

      <h2 class="text-white text-4xl mb-6">How we integrate with your team</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap w-full lg:flex-nowrap">
      <div
        class="bg-navy-light flex mb-6 p-6 w-full lg:mr-6 lg:p-12 lg:w-1/3"
        itemscope
        itemtype="http://schema.org/Service"
        data-aos="fade-up"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col w-full">
          <Icon class="h-20 inline-block mb-12 w-20" name="icons/retainer" />

          <h3 class="text-white text-xl mb-4" itemprop="name">
            The Ship Shape Retainer Model
          </h3>

          <p class="flex flex-grow text-white">
            We want to remain available for you throughout your projects. Our
            retainer ensures your company has Ship Shapeâ€™s full attention for a
            couple of hours per week. Our on-demand retainer model includes pair
            programming and coaching for your team.
          </p>

          <a class="btn btn-white text-center" href="/contact/"> Learn more</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="bg-navy-light flex mb-6 p-6 w-full lg:mr-6 lg:p-12 lg:w-1/3"
        itemscope
        itemtype="http://schema.org/Service"
        data-aos="fade-up"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col w-full">
          <Icon class="h-20 inline-block mb-12 w-20" name="icons/staff" />

          <h3 class="text-white text-xl mb-4" itemprop="name">
            Staff Augmentation
          </h3>

          <p class="flex flex-grow text-white">
            Consider us a part of your team, serving as added support and
            on-demand Ember.js experts. Ship Shape joins you in the race to
            complete your project milestones, boost your current workflow or
            lend our expertise in Ember.
          </p>

          <a class="btn btn-white text-center" href="/contact/">
            Let's Build Together
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="bg-navy-light flex mb-6 p-6 w-full lg:mr-6 lg:p-12 lg:w-1/3"
        itemscope
        itemtype="http://schema.org/Service"
        data-aos="fade-up"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col w-full">
          <Icon class="h-20 inline-block mb-12 w-20" name="icons/mentor" />

          <h3 class="text-white text-xl mb-4" itemprop="name">
            Learn the ropes
          </h3>

          <p class="flex flex-grow text-white">
            Ship Shape created one-on-one programs for in-depth team training
            and mentoring. We help your company refine your skills in the latest
            in Javascript, code writing and Ember.js. development.
          </p>

          <a class="btn btn-white text-center" href="/contact/">
            Sign Up for Team Training
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
